    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of Bavarian engineering. Powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, the powerplant features high-pressure individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The ZF 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior mechanical grip. This chassis has received preventative subframe reinforcement and a full cooling system refresh. With factory-spec compression across all cylinders and a pristine underside, this vehicle maintains its original torsional rigidity and kinematic excellence. A concours-level specimen for the discerning purist.",
